Date: Tue, 27 Aug 2024 21:25:16 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 069/194] stalled! ASoC: codecs: cs35l36: include
 SND_SOC_DAIFMT_DSP_B support

Tested in Google Pixel 3. Both SND_SOC_DAIFMT_DSP_A and SND_SOC_DAIFMT_DSP_B works fine.

Signed-off-by: Joel Selvaraj <foss@joelselvaraj.com>
---
 sound/soc/codecs/cs35l36.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/sound/soc/codecs/cs35l36.c b/sound/soc/codecs/cs35l36.c
index 93818d7ec1a7..0218f7f964df 100644
--- a/sound/soc/codecs/cs35l36.c
+++ b/sound/soc/codecs/cs35l36.c
@@ -793,6 +793,7 @@ static int cs35l36_set_dai_fmt(struct snd_soc_dai *component_dai,
 
 	switch (fmt & SND_SOC_DAIFMT_FORMAT_MASK) {
 	case SND_SOC_DAIFMT_DSP_A:
+	case SND_SOC_DAIFMT_DSP_B:
 		asp_fmt = 0;
 		break;
 	case SND_SOC_DAIFMT_I2S:
